>>b741bf84-4928-4289-8d1f-60c879358dda
I'm a brainlet. What the heck's going on with the El Paso shooter?

So before the shooting, he was a democrat, right? Is this snapshot taken from some kind of alternative to Facebook? Also, if democrats are the ones that fight for more government programs to help black people, why would a democrat go into a place populated by ethnic minorities and start blasting? And then, there's the change in his profile after the shooting. Did he self-report this and then the changes were made later by someone else?

Who is this mysterious "Q Anon" I keep reading about all the time?

The most confusing thing of all: what was the purpose of the shooting and through what steps was the purpose fulfilled?

What do we know about the Dayton and Ohio shootings? Can I ask about those in this thread or is that off-topic?
